{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Conduct a review into the treatment of white people by the police ",
        "additional_details": "We believe some recent high profile cases are raising concerns that the policing response to white people is below adequate. The government needs to review this to see whether this is happening and if so, why it is happening.",
        "background": "We call on the government to conduct a review into whether there are internal or external factors that are impacting police services and how they respond to white people, particularly if the police are discriminatory towards white people.",
